DarkMouse::

She looked as th explosion happened. She watched it engulf the body 
of Quickstrike.  She closed her eyes and let a single tear fall down 
her cheek. Good Bye old friend, she thought. Then she got a strange 
idea.  She would wait until they had left and she would go and get a 
DNA sample from the body and clone him. Like she was doing already 
for KitKat, she could do for Quickstrike. 

She would wait, and then bring back her friend.
